abstract_ssm: ACT-UAW Local 7902 represents over 4,000 part-time and adjunct teachers at the New School and New York University. This collection is consists of the websites for Local 7902, dating back to 2013. The union is made-up of four bargaining units, the New York University Adjuncts, New School Part-Time Faculty (PTF), New School Student Employees (SENS), and New School Student Health Services Employees (SHENS).
